<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
	<head>
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: sans-serif;
				background-color: white;
				color: #202124;
			}
			p {
				line-height: 1.5;
			}
			ul li {
				line-height: 1.5;
			}
		</style>

	</head>

	<body>
		<p>Hello {{NAME}}!</p>
		<p>Your <b>{{EVENT_NAME}}</b> is scheduled. Below are the details for your upcoming event</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Location: {{LOCATION}} </li>
			<li>Description: {{DESCRIPTION}} </li>
			<li>Date: {{CHOSEN_DATE}} </li>
			<li>Meeting Start Time: {{START_TIME}}</li>
			<li>Duration: {{DURATION}} minutes </li>
		</ul>
		<p>If you like to reschedule or cancel, please reply back to this email.</p>
		<div>
			<p>Looking forward to seeing you soon! </p>
			<p>Sincerely, <br> The Qoom Team</p>
		</div>
	</body>

</html>
